  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to investigate clinical non-inferiority, pharmacodynamic effect
      and safety of Actparin® (heparin sodium - Laboratório Químico Farmacêutico Bergamo Ltd.)
      compared to Heparin Sodium (APP Pharmaceuticals) in patients with renal failure under
      hemodialysis treatment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
